313
00:18:21,270 --> 00:18:23,680
Father, a tree won't grow straight
without pruning,

314
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:25,240
and a person won't succeed
without teaching.

315
00:18:25,240 --> 00:18:25,640
Right.

316
00:18:30,920 --> 00:18:33,880
