Let's resort to the punishing rod.

317
00:18:34,220 --> 00:18:34,980
Xilou.

318
00:18:39,720 --> 00:18:42,330
A child's misbehavior
is also the mother's fault.

319
00:18:42,330 --> 00:18:43,970
Why don't you let me, his mother,

