360
00:20:34,270 --> 00:20:35,760
You silly child.

361
00:20:36,210 --> 00:20:38,870
What are you doing?
Are you cursing your mother?

362
00:20:40,840 --> 00:20:43,730
Mother, it's so good to see you.

363
00:20:45,880 --> 00:20:47,940
